name: Gatekeeper - B/W
description:
Freezing rain coats rural power lines at the edge of a forest during an outage.

There are so many barriers to access, information, connection, power, time. Capturing this moment as the rain coated every inch of my surroundings in a fragile crystalline layer was dazzling. A few moments of creative exploration before emergency preparation. 

2016. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing and greyscale.

1024x685 300dpi jpg
